@node "wasmacht" "A1"
 
  These 2 Pics contain a lot of title screens from the very
  best C64 games.
 
  Use them in conjunction with WBPattern or what you want.

  You need at least a screen in Super HighRes Interlace
  to view them perfectly.  

  If you`ve any comments don`t hesitate to email me at:
  Winfried.Falkenhahn@informatik.fh-fulda.de! 

  Or just have a visit on my c00l homepage (coming soon)!!

@endnode

